{"title":"Amiodarona-2024-1","guid":"","filepath":"/Users/criaah/Vault/📚 Resources/Mapas-Mentales/Entidades clínicas/Cardiología/Amiodarona-2024-1.smmx","root":{"id":"0","parent":"-1","text":"- Amiodarona","guid":"mavor8SivbcU8H19GVEiMQ","children":[{"id":"1","parent":"0","text":"Resumen\\Nfarmacodinámico","guid":"kPmM02_8y9SKaEm8b-Tpbg","children":[{"id":"2","parent":"1","text":"• Mecanismo principal: Efecto antiarrítmico bloqueando canales de K+ dependientes de voltaje\\N→ prolongación de la repolarización del potencial de acción cardíaco.","guid":"fOLt5NLp6uvgOuGreZUznw","children":[]},{"id":"3","parent":"1","text":"• Mecanismo secundario: Inhibe receptores β, canales de Na+ y Ca++\\N→ ↓ conducción a través del nodo AV y nodo sinusal.","guid":"zWLauHB8Ea5xyP36imgkiQ","children":[]},{"id":"4","parent":"1","text":"• Usos especiales: Único antiarrítmico con casi nulo efecto inotrópico negativo\\N→ uso en pacientes con FE reducida.","guid":"XnwwVmIHNDXA4FRP-OLOrg","children":[]}]},{"id":"5","parent":"0","text":"Efectos adversos de\\Nla Amiodarona","guid":"","children":[{"id":"6","parent":"5","text":"Resumen general • Alta eficacia, pero limitada al uso a\\Ncorto plazo debido a su perfil de efectos secundarios.","guid":"-hKqrAMd8McA7NoNGB8sLg","children":[]},{"id":"7","parent":"5","text":"• Acumulación en tejidos → daño en tiroides, pulmones, nervios, piel, ojos y corazón.","guid":"1BA-qlQNxRIGKAbjcDDf3w","children":[]},{"id":"8","parent":"5","text":"• Administrar la dosis más baja efectiva.","guid":"NtRaYucKxQ2FENLvzh8VqQ","children":[]},{"id":"9","parent":"5","text":"• Evaluaciones iniciales: ECG, Rx tórax, exámenes\\Noftalmológicos, función tiroidea, hepática y pulmonar.","guid":"FElPvwlc7x5dsrRyjlC2Pw","children":[]},{"id":"10","parent":"5","text":"• Monitoreo: Función tiroidea y hepática c/3-6 meses, ECG anual.","guid":"gBSZWI69BJTKQozFXtzOjQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"11","parent":"0","text":"Efectos adversos\\Npor sistemas","guid":"","children":[{"id":"12","parent":"11","text":"Pulmonar","guid":"qw-CRdHna4Z6dktRuvO1Ww","children":[{"id":"13","parent":"12","text":"• Fibrosis pulmonar","guid":"f4yvtCFJvH7ajM445KQTDQ","children":[]},{"id":"14","parent":"12","text":"• Neumonitis intersticial crónica","guid":"NU-ISVm7-mf_iTj5qnpeQA","children":[]},{"id":"15","parent":"12","text":"• Neumonía organizada","guid":"M8KRLoCxu9tMEz1RebY1Mg","children":[]},{"id":"16","parent":"12","text":"• SDRA","guid":"UN77s72fQup-P9cc6KV_9A","children":[]},{"id":"17","parent":"12","text":"• Masa pulmonar solitaria","guid":"vkjSqObgR66eOCg3wYwAuw","children":[]}]},{"id":"18","parent":"11","text":"Tiroides","guid":"H3iYDP59i4zLgVIGs7AZ9Q","children":[{"id":"19","parent":"18","text":"• Hipotiroidismo","guid":"aNisDl1Wf95YvrJlgYoLfg","children":[]},{"id":"20","parent":"18","text":"• Hipertiroidismo/tirotoxicosis","guid":"YZMP-GSO1a1mY4SLRX9Swg","children":[]},{"id":"21","parent":"18","text":"• Exacerbación de patologías tiroideas preexistentes","guid":"x_wcxB_7-URuwH-jdRJ5Xw","children":[]}]},{"id":"22","parent":"11","text":"Hepático","guid":"-g5NjmuQ3jwnHssD9JyWYQ","children":[{"id":"23","parent":"22","text":"• ↑ AST y/o ALT > 2x normal","guid":"M2t41nAsHIG6VnZHyzDy3g","children":[]},{"id":"24","parent":"22","text":"• Hepatitis y cirrosis","guid":"m6h3eTYaSxriKIvtF1Gb4Q","children":[]}]},{"id":"25","parent":"11","text":"Cardíaco","guid":"NvdFQ5ZV_sPerSTvd_kJ_g","children":[{"id":"26","parent":"25","text":"• Proarritmia","guid":"DsV2sXXBeuHaq7bWEDtGOw","children":[]},{"id":"27","parent":"25","text":"• Bradicardia y bloqueo AV","guid":"ncYh-4yZNBRsKKnPB_e0xQ","children":[]},{"id":"28","parent":"25","text":"• Hipotensión","guid":"UErEjyQOHki8cv5ZAVxWjw","children":[]}]},{"id":"29","parent":"11","text":"Ocular","guid":"Y8da1fplN3mdqSMXR20w1A","children":[{"id":"30","parent":"29","text":"• Microdepósitos corneales","guid":"cj3OVRBheEwjJPCAzqQTFQ","children":[]},{"id":"31","parent":"29","text":"• Neuritis óptica","guid":"LvrTKFO8QkLhiuxa9Z6Eog","children":[]}]},{"id":"32","parent":"11","text":"Gastrointestinal","guid":"daD3LeFgWJaaFkya91bpFA","children":[{"id":"33","parent":"32","text":"• Náuseas","guid":"3zqd-AiqOlP16Vg2ZmdXUA","children":[]},{"id":"34","parent":"32","text":"• Anorexia","guid":"DnB6P2eX84QcgiAcYu9aQA","children":[]},{"id":"35","parent":"32","text":"• Estreñimiento","guid":"g4elCqsLXDp_mOtQybzHcw","children":[]}]},{"id":"36","parent":"11","text":"Dermatológico","guid":"gScndwQlvOFm4cp1GYhwmA","children":[{"id":"37","parent":"36","text":"• Fotosensibilidad","guid":"AuNrPL2gmczmSPW6YF0Waw","children":[]},{"id":"38","parent":"36","text":"• Coloración azulada de la piel","guid":"AXSg6veEaC_3i8t4eZjlsQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"39","parent":"11","text":"CNS","guid":"zhtuElVAGUyMwSBQgIoltA","children":[{"id":"40","parent":"39","text":"• Neuropatía periférica","guid":"T7kC5Zz1GqZW1ESmQp7dCA","children":[]},{"id":"41","parent":"39","text":"• Ataxia","guid":"I-U_1K1tFP9YyQMWO789bg","children":[]},{"id":"42","parent":"39","text":"• Parestesia","guid":"rCoUiT6V_vG0CS5yLYE5zw","children":[]},{"id":"43","parent":"39","text":"• Trastornos del sueño","guid":"2jRCjeXtVN69TflONL48Jg","children":[]},{"id":"44","parent":"39","text":"• Déficit de memoria","guid":"-gCTnaHMiTn6l0WOrK0hFQ","children":[]},{"id":"45","parent":"39","text":"• Temblor","guid":"wK5iVWDaHG1WrFMMQ5m_WQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"46","parent":"11","text":"Genitourinario","guid":"kqulgVrJC2t9kE8MT1ui5w","children":[{"id":"47","parent":"46","text":"• Epididimitis","guid":"_bziyq7EWUW3XyBrb-thfA","children":[]},{"id":"48","parent":"46","text":"• Disfunción eréctil","guid":"xx4BsDE2C91fjGp-bdc5dw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"49","parent":"0","text":"Pulmonar","guid":"vUHG_TX7Zn_StJIDA9Rieg","children":[{"id":"50","parent":"49","text":"• Toxicidad pulmonar inducida por amiodarona → principal\\Ncausa de muertes asociadas al tratamiento con amiodarona.","guid":"58QEHAQIx2YjRFV_ybXxaQ","children":[]},{"id":"51","parent":"49","text":"• La toxicidad se correlaciona más con la dosis\\Nacumulada que con los niveles séricos del fármaco.","guid":"19hktBNxRrSO6rBBYvCrqw","children":[]},{"id":"52","parent":"49","text":"• Tratamiento: Suspender amiodarona + iniciar terapia con corticosteroides.","guid":"Ldqe0OldJU1Kz1gzmbJmIg","children":[]}]},{"id":"53","parent":"0","text":"Tiroides","guid":"JjSRIa-2F5SCNK4D3HLIOA","children":[{"id":"54","parent":"53","text":"• Disfunción tiroidea en ∼10% de pacientes con tratamiento prolongado (n).","guid":"Uy82-I5GmDWmQoS1dhJ3fQ","children":[]},{"id":"55","parent":"53","text":"Hipotiroidismo inducido\\Npor amiodarona","guid":"xk8fupEi9sDaycr4I4incA","children":[{"id":"56","parent":"55","text":"◦ Fisiopatología:","guid":"MHgU9_UmtDdxOun9doEGIA","children":[{"id":"57","parent":"56","text":"▪ ↑ Contenido de I en amiodarona → inhibición de la\\Nbiosíntesis de hormonas tiroideas (efecto Wolff-Chaikoff).","guid":"IZpXJ8LLpcVnJBok0wPNgQ","children":[]},{"id":"58","parent":"56","text":"▪ Amiodarona → inhibición de la conversión\\Nperiférica de T4 a T3 → ↑ rT3 inactiva.","guid":"Iaa6KSdL1WlDzyUgkNPQ-g","children":[]}]},{"id":"59","parent":"55","text":"◦ Tratamiento: Sustitución hormonal tiroidea (levotiroxina).","guid":"Gk1rGwBp0_S2zgAf9Gr1sA","children":[]}]},{"id":"60","parent":"53","text":"Tirotoxicosis inducida\\Npor amiodarona","guid":"cJAB2QTogVVX3rY5HBYWQA","children":[{"id":"61","parent":"60","text":"• Tipo I","guid":"8Y0bBmccSeZ_7ms2CMureQ","children":[{"id":"62","parent":"61","text":"◦ Fisiopatología: ↑ I contenido en amiodarona → ↑ síntesis y\\Nliberación de hormonas tiroideas (fenómeno de Jod-Basedow).","guid":"MqsV89SjhMYNIlRdlzd3lw","children":[]},{"id":"63","parent":"61","text":"◦ Tratamiento: Antitiroideos (ej., tionamidas); si es\\Nresistente → radioyodo o tiroidectomía quirúrgica.","guid":"kJqaYVBn8V8vnlXWmApuIw","children":[]}]},{"id":"64","parent":"60","text":"• Tipo II","guid":"AsA4tb418ECmwI_LD0jVNg","children":[{"id":"65","parent":"64","text":"◦ Fisiopatología: Daño inducido por el fármaco en células foliculares →\\Ntiroiditis destructiva → ↑ liberación de hormonas tiroideas preformadas.","guid":"_YlsCzlmsugq7iqLWxKZxA","children":[]},{"id":"66","parent":"64","text":"◦ Tratamiento: Terapia con glucocorticoides.","guid":"WiHQiNIgmgz_nJx1v0_MHA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"67","parent":"0","text":"Hepático","guid":"eM8RSeAvM6QXROjo6k85AQ","children":[{"id":"68","parent":"67","text":"• Elevación asintomática de AST y ALT\\Nes común tras el inicio de amiodarona.","guid":"s4UO3TPpNMq8FZF18Q7YNg","children":[]},{"id":"69","parent":"67","text":"• Suspender amiodarona si AST y/o\\NALT ↑ > 2x el rango normal.","guid":"67ZuN_8ojOKz-Z_0eUUiMA","children":[]}]},{"id":"70","parent":"0","text":"Cardíaco","guid":"","children":[{"id":"71","parent":"70","text":"• ↓ Frecuencia cardíaca y conducción en nodo AV\\N→ actividad bloqueadora de canales de Ca++.","guid":"6aU5RdH4g9AfOQZoLS0dnA","children":[]},{"id":"72","parent":"70","text":"• Puede causar prolongación del QT, pero bajo\\Nriesgo de progresión a torsades de pointes.","guid":"Q-7xfjXES-fufF50VnUCAw","children":[]}]},{"id":"73","parent":"0","text":"Ocular","guid":"","children":[{"id":"74","parent":"73","text":"• Microdepósitos corneales en >90% de pacientes, generalmente asintomáticos, pero\\Npueden causar visión en halo (especialmente nocturna), fotofobia y visión borrosa.","guid":"U3_kV_UGmNdcs6x2OgthrA","children":[]}]},{"id":"75","parent":"0","text":"Indicaciones de la\\NAmiodarona","guid":"","children":[{"id":"76","parent":"75","text":"Tratamiento agudo\\N(administración IV)","guid":"T-BhnGDROLSVDdh1145wzQ","children":[{"id":"77","parent":"76","text":"• Segunda línea en pacientes con taquicardia ventricular\\N(TV) hemodinámicamente estables.","guid":"7guvrPKReAr7Y3D2Aj60Nw","children":[]},{"id":"78","parent":"76","text":"• TV persistente después de desfibrilación.","guid":"shcT1lOln-fgaLxGyRg_Wg","children":[]},{"id":"79","parent":"76","text":"• Fibrilación ventricular sin pulso.","guid":"mhTdNELPiMhENGjJGb-A8w","children":[]},{"id":"80","parent":"76","text":"• Taquicardia supraventricular en pacientes con\\Ninsuficiencia cardíaca (FEVI < 40%).","guid":"2IsrXoDdFVBbwMI1c6fvdQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"81","parent":"75","text":"Tratamiento a largo plazo\\N(administración oral)","guid":"lzH1NuH-ATueg-7uyQKvyA","children":[{"id":"82","parent":"81","text":"• Control del ritmo en fibrilación auricular sintomática refractaria (arritmia supraventricular) y\\Ncardiopatía subyacente → restauración y mantenimiento del ritmo sinusal.","guid":"Giv_Bd8iS2LdVjI8uqAGRg","children":[]},{"id":"83","parent":"81","text":"• Fármaco de elección para arritmias supraventriculares en la mayoría\\Nde los pacientes con insuficiencia cardíaca (FEVI < 40%).","guid":"DWRYZKA9xdM-bCJbuYR7Uw","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"84","parent":"0","text":"Contraindicaciones de\\Nla Amiodarona","guid":"","children":[{"id":"85","parent":"84","text":"• Disfunción severa del nodo sinusal con bradicardia sinusal marcada.","guid":"DjNedvMalWxT4J7xYAD8SA","children":[]},{"id":"86","parent":"84","text":"• Bloqueo cardíaco de segundo y tercer grado\\N(excepto en pacientes con marcapasos funcional).","guid":"cYiDC6V2Jz3FMKwmX_hMng","children":[]},{"id":"87","parent":"84","text":"• Hipertiroidismo e hipotiroidismo.","guid":"JxIEPwzA5KL0Q75G_Iw8SQ","children":[]},{"id":"88","parent":"84","text":"• Alergia conocida al yodo.","guid":"wfuVjTYcyK3Eu5Rc0dKLgA","children":[]},{"id":"89","parent":"84","text":"• Enfermedad pulmonar preexistente.","guid":"zGfDhM6Q4JfYy2jUHgs0cw","children":[]}]},{"id":"90","parent":"0","text":"Interacciones de la\\NAmiodarona","guid":"oQTPUw4qRR8i5HL-5WHdlQ","children":[{"id":"91","parent":"90","text":"• Amiodarona inhibe las enzimas del citocromo P450 → ↓ depuración de los siguientes fármacos:","guid":"WVL5BMVSP5B6zVFm8lMg-w","children":[]},{"id":"92","parent":"90","text":"◦ Warfarina → ↑ riesgo de hemorragia.","guid":"XbaTpTxWWlgWfnPPL6cZbw","children":[]},{"id":"93","parent":"90","text":"◦ Simvastatina → ↑ riesgo de rabdomiólisis.","guid":"9D8TySD8MLO7i1UNgfD33w","children":[]},{"id":"94","parent":"90","text":"◦ Digoxina.","guid":"WZLvEl-4zOoPlqQJp_r02w","children":[]},{"id":"95","parent":"90","text":"◦ Ciclosporina.","guid":"c-SNYvcDEhVfuSoU9E08Rg","children":[]},{"id":"96","parent":"90","text":"◦ Flecainida, procainamida, quinidina.","guid":"MUFKjiCNn-ayDfN2yqHEyQ","children":[]},{"id":"97","parent":"90","text":"◦ Sildenafilo.","guid":"rf9IVmW0A8lePGGr1afptQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"98","parent":"0","text":"Farmacocinética de\\Nla Amiodarona","guid":"","children":[{"id":"99","parent":"98","text":"• Propiedades lipofílicas → acumulación en miocardio y músculos\\N→ larga duración de acción.","guid":"IaX_fJ8V9iWHfM5jr-VjeQ","children":[]},{"id":"100","parent":"98","text":"• Metabolismo hepático por CYP3A4 → excreción biliar.","guid":"BVqWMYLvfWbC22ZzsHSdTQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"101","parent":"0","text":"Tratamiento oral","guid":"rrvx9TaMwX8NGRFhnHDGVg","children":[{"id":"102","parent":"101","text":"• Inicio de acción: 2 días a 3 semanas.","guid":"qh9SmWDe6vlCil1oZuQu4g","children":[]},{"id":"103","parent":"101","text":"• Tiempo hasta el efecto máximo: 1 semana a 5 meses.","guid":"frxYy9bIyO-LyCFbrAr5zg","children":[]},{"id":"104","parent":"101","text":"• Vida media de eliminación: 40-55 días.","guid":"ZK9Qi-ptTnHa2K8PUeUeig","children":[]}]},{"id":"105","parent":"0","text":"Bolo IV","guid":"","children":[{"id":"106","parent":"105","text":"• Inicio de acción: dentro de pocas horas.","guid":"DRg0SM_3ZLBI3mAh2aGzAg","children":[]},{"id":"107","parent":"105","text":"• Tiempo hasta el efecto máximo: 15 minutos.","guid":"d3ncV64u95FWxc1CZN9WJg","children":[]},{"id":"108","parent":"105","text":"• Vida media de eliminación: 9-36 días.","guid":"attjJ_zh8rrJ9dm1TxXSRw","children":[]}]}]},"node_count":108,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Cardiología","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Cardiología","filename":"Amiodarona-2024-1","id":"map_221","resolved_references":[]}